      <content><![CDATA[<p>OpenCms 10.5 comes with a rewritten power-user backoffice called the Workplace.&nbsp;</p>
<p>With improved inline editing options such as <strong>drag &amp; drop for images</strong> it's easier than ever for content manager to create great looking websites with OpenCms.</p>
<p>Check out the <a href="%(link0)">tutorial</a> for a quick intro&nbsp;about the use of the&nbsp;editing features.</p>]]></content>
